{
  "stem": "20035.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Allied forces bombed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Basically, in three days there's no more factory left.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, let's call it the first time that we-- we called it that Red Cross packages were falling from the sky.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm not sure they were bombs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were not Red Cross packages.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we-- we had the feeling that we are coming towards-- towards Allied victory.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We are coming to the victory.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We are coming to the end of the suffering, although by already this time, which was sometime the end of March of 1945, by this time I was weak.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was-- my brother was a lot less stronger and in a bad shape.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But somehow we had a feeling that we have a-- we have a hope.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We have a chance.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We have-- we had something to look forwards.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Before we heard sometimes some kind of gunshots, but very little.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But these three days was the confirmation of strength, the confirmation of who is really the master.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "First day, they started us to put us back to work and tried to pull out some equipment and this one.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then the bombs came again at the end of that second day and the third day in the morning.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Finally, they emptied the camp and we-- they put us on the road marching.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "This marching was the most horrendous thing, because we marched day and-- practically day and night why the-- while our guards had the motorcycles, the cars, the trucks.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we were on the road just marching.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the-- the march was like a death march.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was really a death march, because anybody who get at the end of the line, forget about not being able to cope-- cope or get-- lie down or not to go.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
